{"id":15254,"date":"2022-12-31T04:09:35","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:09:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-tp-hcm.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:09:35","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:09:35","slug":"khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-tp-hcm-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-tp-hcm-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng l\u00e1i th\u1eed VF 8 t\u1ea1i TP.HCM"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng TP.HCM \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao xe \u0111i\u1ec7n VF 8 v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u00ean trong cabin v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, ng\u00e0y 28\/10.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">B\u1ecf l\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e1i th\u1eed xe VF 8 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i TP.HCM v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7, anh Nguy\u1ec5n Minh S\u01a1n c\u00f9ng v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 con trai 10 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i Paragon Tower (3 Nguy\u1ec5n L\u01b0\u01a1ng B\u1eb1ng, P.T\u00e2n Ph\u00fa, Q.7). ) s\u00e1ng 28\/10, l\u00e1i th\u1eed m\u1eabu \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a VinFast.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong ba ng\u00e0y, t\u1eeb 28 \u0111\u1ebfn 30\/10, g\u1ea7n Trung t\u00e2m H\u1ed9i ch\u1ee3 v\u00e0 Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (SECC), n\u01a1i \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd l\u00e1i th\u1eed VF 8 t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg\" title=\"khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd l\u00e1i th\u1eed VF 8 t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1edd l\u00e1i th\u1eed c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 100. V\u00ec \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua xe n\u00ean anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1eabu xe \u0111i\u1ec7n cao c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u201cNh\u00ecn t\u1eeb xa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra VF 8 b\u1edfi ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng, \u200b\u200bkh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn. C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y\u201d, v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u01a1n 15 n\u0103m c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i cho bi\u1ebft.  n\u0103m nay cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201c\u0110u\u00f4i xe c\u1ee7a VF 8 mang phong c\u00e1ch coupe th\u1ec3 thao, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n LED s\u00e2u, s\u1eafc c\u1ea1nh, gi\u00fap xe t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"D\u00e0n VF 8 t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e1i th\u1eed.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_180_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg\" title=\"1672454525_180_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_180_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_180_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_180_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">D\u00e0n VF 8 t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e1i th\u1eed.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ngo\u00e0i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1eaft m\u1eaft, anh Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf Ho\u00e0ng (qu\u1eadn 4) chia s\u1ebb, anh t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.  \u201cKh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a VF 8 r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1eabu SUV c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac h\u1ea1ng D m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u1ea7m l\u00e1i. Kho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n ph\u00eda sau kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i\u201d, anh Th\u1ebf Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1.  \u201cVF 8 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trung t\u00e2m l\u1edbn, b\u1eaft m\u1eaft. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00e1c ph\u00edm b\u1ea5m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7.\u201d<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Sau khi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m xe t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a VF 8. \u201cXe t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi xe m\u00e1y x\u0103ng, \u00eam v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd\u201d.  Anh Ph\u1ea1m Qu\u1ed1c Anh (B\u00ecnh Th\u1ea1nh) chia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ea1y th\u1eed xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.  \u201cTrong t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a VF 8, hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 m\u1eabu xe m\u00e1y x\u0103ng n\u00e0o c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh linh ho\u1ea1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u00e1i th\u1eed xe VinFast VF 8.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_335_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg\" title=\"1672454525_335_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_335_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_335_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_335_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng l\u00e1i th\u1eed xe VinFast VF 8.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">X\u00e9t c\u00e1c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed t\u1eeb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 VF 8 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n.  M\u1eabu xe c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean HUD, gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n 12 h\u01b0\u1edbng, d\u00e0n \u00e2m thanh 12 loa, t\u00ednh n\u0103ng l\u00e0m m\u00e1t h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n Plus v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ADAS, Smart Service\u2026 \u201cSo v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng xe x\u0103ng c\u00f9ng t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 , t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y\u201d, anh Qu\u1ed1c Anh cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201cS\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch tr\u00ean VF 8 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc khi ch\u1ecdn mua xe m\u00e1y x\u0103ng t\u1ea7m gi\u00e1 1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Sau khi c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eed, anh Minh S\u01a1n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ecdc m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y.  Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean, anh cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1eed chi\u1ebfc VF e34 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n xe l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u00ean ch\u1edd th\u1eed tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp chi\u1ebfc VF 8 r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7t mua.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"M\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb7t mua chi\u1ebfc VF 8 sau khi l\u00e1i th\u1eed.\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_399_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg\" title=\"1672454525_399_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_399_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_399_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672454525_399_khach-hang-viet-hao-hung-lai-thu-vf-8-tai.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">M\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1eb7t mua chi\u1ebfc VF 8 sau khi l\u00e1i th\u1eed.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, VF 8 c\u00f3 hai t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Eco v\u00e0 Plus, gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 1,109 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 1,289 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT.  M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a bao g\u1ed3m chi ph\u00ed s\u1edf h\u1eefu pin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn g\u00f3i thu\u00ea pin t\u00f9y theo nhu c\u1ea7u.  Ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a VF 8 khi s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ea7y l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 460 \u2013 510 km, theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Hi\u1ec7n xe \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i nh\u01b0 thu\u1ebf TT\u0110B 3% cho \u00f4 t\u00f4 d\u01b0\u1edbi 9 ch\u1ed7, 0% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Tu\u1ea5n V\u0169<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">\u1ea2nh: VinFast.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng TP.HCM \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao xe \u0111i\u1ec7n VF 8 v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb9p, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 b\u00ean trong cabin v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, ng\u00e0y 28\/10. B\u1ecf l\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e1i th\u1eed xe VF 8 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i TP.HCM v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7, anh Nguy\u1ec5n Minh S\u01a1n c\u00f9ng v\u1ee3 v\u00e0 con trai 10 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15255,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15254"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15254"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15254\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15255"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15254"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15254"},{"taxonomy":"post_